(93,	1,	'2026-07-03 12:37:53',	'2026-07-03 11:37:53',	'<!-- wp:acf/hero-panel {\"name\":\"acf/hero-panel\",\"data\":{\"hero_heading\":\"About Us\",\"_hero_heading\":\"field_6a465aa9ac58a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/two-column-panel {\"name\":\"acf/two-column-panel\",\"data\":{\"heading\":\"Fully Licensed Flights\",\"_heading\":\"field_6a47e23efca24\",\"column_one\":\"\\u003cp class=\'intro\'\\u003eWe will make sure you get the best service possible, because the last thing you need is to feel stressed about your transfer. We are a professional, experienced and safe operator.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eFlights-Holbox is one of the few operators in the Riviera Maya offering fully licensed flights (air taxis) or vans (ground transfer), with more than 17 years of experience.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"_column_one\":\"field_6a47e256fca26\",\"column_two\":\"\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eOur planes only fly between 7:00 and 17:30. Flight times can change depending on season and daylight \\u0026mdash; it\\u0026rsquo;s not possible to fly to Holbox at night.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eHolbox flights use the FBO at the International Airport of Canc\\u0026uacute;n.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThere\\u0026rsquo;s a free shuttle between the terminals every 30 minutes that can take you to and from the FBO.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eYou can also just take a taxi for around 20\\u0026ndash;30 USD (5 minute ride).\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIf you\\u0026rsquo;re flying out of Canc\\u0026uacute;n airport you\\u0026rsquo;ll need to pay an airport tax of 162 pesos (or 8 USD) \\u0026mdash; unless you\\u0026rsquo;re flying into and out of Canc\\u0026uacute;n airport on the same day.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThere are only a few ATMs on Isla Holbox, so we suggest bringing enough cash to the island.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eWe accept card payments, bank transfer or PayPal only \\u0026mdash; no cash payments possible.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eYou can get to the FBO airport in Canc\\u0026uacute;n only by taxi or the free shuttle bus \\u0026mdash; you can\\u0026rsquo;t walk.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\",\"_column_two\":\"field_6a47e26dfca28\",\"pullout_summary\":\"With Flights Holbox you choose a professional company you can rely on, with a well-priced service. We will take you safely and comfortably to your final destination.\",\"_pullout_summary\":\"field_6a47e277fca29\"},\"mode\":\"preview\"} /-->',	'About Us',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'about-us',	'',	'',	'2026-07-03 17:40:00',	'2026-07-03 16:40:00',	'',	0,	'http://flightsholboxv1.local/?page_id=93',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
