(183,	1,	'2026-07-03 17:36:19',	'2026-07-03 16:36:19',	'<!-- wp:acf/hero-panel {\"name\":\"acf/hero-panel\",\"data\":{\"hero_heading\":\"About Us\",\"_hero_heading\":\"field_6a465aa9ac58a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/two-column-panel {\"name\":\"acf/two-column-panel\",\"data\":{\"heading\":\"Fully Licensed Flights\",\"_heading\":\"field_6a47e23efca24\",\"column_one\":\"<p class=\"intro\">We will make sure you get the best service possible, because the last thing you need is to feel stressed about your transfer. We are a professional, experienced and safe operator.</p><p>Flights-Holbox is one of the few operators in the Riviera Maya offering fully licensed flights (air taxis) or vans (ground transfer), with more than 17 years of experience.</p>\",\"_column_one\":\"field_6a47e256fca26\",\"column_two\":\"<ul><li>Our planes only fly between 7:00 and 17:30. Flight times can change depending on season and daylight &mdash; it&rsquo;s not possible to fly to Holbox at night.</li><li>Holbox flights use the FBO at the International Airport of Canc&uacute;n.</li><li>There&rsquo;s a free shuttle between the terminals every 30 minutes that can take you to and from the FBO.</li><li>You can also just take a taxi for around 20&ndash;30 USD (5 minute ride).</li><li>If you&rsquo;re flying out of Canc&uacute;n airport you&rsquo;ll need to pay an airport tax of 162 pesos (or 8 USD) &mdash; unless you&rsquo;re flying into and out of Canc&uacute;n airport on the same day.</li><li>There are only a few ATMs on Isla Holbox, so we suggest bringing enough cash to the island.</li><li>We accept card payments, bank transfer or PayPal only &mdash; no cash payments possible.</li><li>You can get to the FBO airport in Canc&uacute;n only by taxi or the free shuttle bus &mdash; you can&rsquo;t walk.</li></ul>\",\"_column_two\":\"field_6a47e26dfca28\",\"pullout_summary\":\"With Flights Holbox you choose a professional company you can rely on, with a well-priced service. We will take you safely and comfortably to your final destination.\",\"_pullout_summary\":\"field_6a47e277fca29\"},\"mode\":\"preview\"} /-->',	'About Us',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'93-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-07-03 17:36:19',	'2026-07-03 16:36:19',	'',	93,	'http://flightsholboxv1.local/?p=183',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
