(186,	1,	'2026-07-03 17:39:35',	'2026-07-03 16:39:35',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Sample Page',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'2-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-07-03 17:39:35',	'2026-07-03 16:39:35',	'',	2,	'http://flightsholboxv1.local/?p=186',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(187,	1,	'2026-07-03 17:40:00',	'2026-07-03 16:40:00',	'<!-- wp:acf/hero-panel {\"name\":\"acf/hero-panel\",\"data\":{\"hero_heading\":\"About Us\",\"_hero_heading\":\"field_6a465aa9ac58a\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/two-column-panel {\"name\":\"acf/two-column-panel\",\"data\":{\"heading\":\"Fully Licensed Flights\",\"_heading\":\"field_6a47e23efca24\",\"column_one\":\"\\u003cp class=\'intro\'\\u003eWe will make sure you get the best service possible, because the last thing you need is to feel stressed about your transfer. We are a professional, experienced and safe operator.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eFlights-Holbox is one of the few operators in the Riviera Maya offering fully licensed flights (air taxis) or vans (ground transfer), with more than 17 years of experience.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"_column_one\":\"field_6a47e256fca26\",\"column_two\":\"\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eOur planes only fly between 7:00 and 17:30. Flight times can change depending on season and daylight \\u0026mdash; it\\u0026rsquo;s not possible to fly to Holbox at night.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eHolbox flights use the FBO at the International Airport of Canc\\u0026uacute;n.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThere\\u0026rsquo;s a free shuttle between the terminals every 30 minutes that can take you to and from the FBO.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eYou can also just take a taxi for around 20\\u0026ndash;30 USD (5 minute ride).\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eIf you\\u0026rsquo;re flying out of Canc\\u0026uacute;n airport you\\u0026rsquo;ll need to pay an airport tax of 162 pesos (or 8 USD) \\u0026mdash; unless you\\u0026rsquo;re flying into and out of Canc\\u0026uacute;n airport on the same day.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eThere are only a few ATMs on Isla Holbox, so we suggest bringing enough cash to the island.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eWe accept card payments, bank transfer or PayPal only \\u0026mdash; no cash payments possible.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003eYou can get to the FBO airport in Canc\\u0026uacute;n only by taxi or the free shuttle bus \\u0026mdash; you can\\u0026rsquo;t walk.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\",\"_column_two\":\"field_6a47e26dfca28\",\"pullout_summary\":\"With Flights Holbox you choose a professional company you can rely on, with a well-priced service. We will take you safely and comfortably to your final destination.\",\"_pullout_summary\":\"field_6a47e277fca29\"},\"mode\":\"preview\"} /-->',	'About Us',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'93-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2026-07-03 17:40:00',	'2026-07-03 16:40:00',	'',	93,	'http://flightsholboxv1.local/?p=187',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
